{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Section_Heading_Gameplay-lg.png?t=1735590058\" />Welcome to the world of Whiffle Blasters, a Twin-Stick Arena Shooter where you only get one shot! If you miss your shot, you better be prepared to slap the competition.<br><br>Balls tend to show up right when you need them, but you will have to fight for each one.  <br>Try to keep track of who shot their ball, and who has been slapped.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1735590058\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Section_Heading_OneShot-lg.png?t=1735590058\" />A shot from the blaster is a one-hit KO, but don\u2019t forget you can knock someone out by slapping them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/oneshot.gif?t=1735590058\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Section_Heading_Slappin-lg.png?t=1735590058\" />A few well timed slaps can be just as effective as a shot!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember: It takes 3 slaps to knock someone out, just like in real life! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Slaps.gif?t=1735590058\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Section_Heading_Geometry-lg.png?t=1735590058\" />Balls tend to ricochet like crazy so watch those angles and bring your protractor! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/geo.gif?t=1735590058\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Section_Heading_LevelUp-lg.png?t=1735590058\" />Did someone say cosmetics? Oh yea, we did.  <br>Win matches to earn XP, level up, and unlock cosmetic items to show off online!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/unlock-loadout2.gif?t=1735590058\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/Section_Heading_Multiplayer-lg.png?t=1735590058\" />Play with up to 4 people online or locally!  <br>Whether your friends are across the globe or right next to you, party up and slap the jeeeez right out of them.... in the game. Just in the game. Plz.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/extras/multiplayer.gif?t=1735590058\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735590058","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/page.bg.jpg?t=1735590058","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735590058","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735590058","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Scre